Class Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • Book

  • public class Book
extends java.lang.Object
    The Book class implements methods to create Book objects, copy them, access them and mutate them. It also contains methods that will print out the information about the Book, the number of Books created and if a Book is equal to another.
